      <title>Cantor Fitzgerald 将启动比特币融资项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/cantor-fitzgerald-to-launch-bitcoin-financing-endeavor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cantor Fitzgerald LP 计划推出比特币融资业务，为拥有加密货币的投资者提供杠杆，加深该投资银行与数字资产领域日益紧密的联系。]]></description>
